------- FILE finalgame.dasm LEVEL 1 PASS 2
      1  10000 ????						;------------------------------------------------
      2  10000 ????						; Cosmic Devourer
      3  10000 ????						; By: Larry Qian
      4  10000 ????						;------------------------------------------------
      5  10000 ????						; Console Switches:
      6  10000 ????						; GAME SELECT:   Cycles starting lives (3, 2, or 1)
      7  10000 ????						;
      8  10000 ????						; GAME RESET:	  Starts the game (from title) / returns to title (in-game)
      9  10000 ????						;------------------------------------------------
